sourcesContent: import { CardMedia, Button, CardActions, CardContent, Typography, Card, Cards } from '@mui/material'; import React from 'react' import '../App.sass'; import { ThemeProvider } from '@mui/material/styles'; import { createTheme } from '@mui/material/styles'; import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid'; import { CardActionArea } from '@mui/material'; const theme = createTheme(); theme.typography.h4 = { fontSize: '22pt', }; theme.typography.h6 = { fontSize: '12pt', }; export default function Articles() { return ( {/* img */} {/* title */} Star Citizen: UI Concept "Aegis Dynamics" {/* description */} For the sake of an article on Millenium Star Citizen, I undertook to recreate the Concept Screen UI shown in the show "Inside Star Citizen". Except for the fonts, I think I did well in 4 hours of work. It' was done on photoshop and illustator. {/* img */} {/* title */} 420 Corp Airsoft - Flyers & Calendar {/* description */} I am a part of the Airsoft team / association based in the Val d'Oise (France) and so I did a couple of Flyers for them and here's the result hope you like it 🙂 {/* img */} {/* title */} Star Citizen - Crusader Industries UI {/* description */} So I made this because I wanted to know where my skills were in terms of speed and it was pretty good, where the Drake UI took me 1 month to do it, this one tuck me just 1 week, so I'm pretty happy🙂 {/* img */} {/* title */} Star Citizen - Drake Interface (Fan made) {/* description */} So I made this because I wanted to know where my skills were in terms of speed and it was pretty good, where the Drake UI took me 1 month to do it, this one tuck me just 1 week, so I'm pretty happy🙂 {/* img */} {/* title */} Black Sheep News {/* description */} A French newspaper about my organisation on the game Star Citizen. Made with La Grande Panthère & Pactole. {/* img */} {/* title */} Star Citizen Patch 3.17 {/* description */} Exemple d'article réalisé chez Millenium. )}
